CK_FLAG_KEY (1 << 5)\n403\t#define MSGPACK_CONTAINER_BIT (1ULL << 62)\n404\t\n405\t/*\n406\t * Search tree packed in array\n407\t */\n408\tstruct ucl_msgpack_parser {\n409\t\tuint8_t prefix;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Prefix byte\t\t\t\t\t*/\n410\t\tuint8_t prefixlen;\t\t\t\t\t/* Length of prefix in bits\t\t*/\n411\t\tuint8_t fmt;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* The desired format \t\t\t*/\n412\t\tuint8_t len;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Length of the object\n413\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  (either length bytes\n414\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  or length of value in case\n415\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  of fixed objects \t\t\t\t*/\n416\t\tuint8_t flags;\t\t\t\t\t\t/* Flags of the specified type\t*/\n417\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_function func;\t/* Parser function\t\t\t\t*/\n418\t} parsers[] = {\n419\t\t{\n420\t\t\t\t0xa0,\n421\t\t\t\t3,\n422\t\t\t\tmsgpack_fixstr,\n423\t\t\t\t0,\n424\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_FIXED|MSGPACK_FLAG_KEY,\n425\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_string\n426\t\t},\n427\t\t{\n428\t\t\t\t0x0,\n429\t\t\t\t1,\n430\t\t\t\tmsgpack_positive_fixint,\n431\t\t\t\t0,\n432\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_FIXED|MSGPACK_FLAG_TYPEVALUE,\n433\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_int\n434\t\t},\n435\t\t{\n436\t\t\t\t0xe0,\n437\t\t\t\t3,\n438\t\t\t\tmsgpack_negative_fixint,\n439\t\t\t\t0,\n440\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_FIXED|MSGPACK_FLAG_TYPEVALUE,\n441\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_int\n442\t\t},\n443\t\t{\n444\t\t\t\t0x80,\n445\t\t\t\t4,\n446\t\t\t\tmsgpack_fixmap,\n447\t\t\t\t0,\n448\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_FIXED|MSGPACK_FLAG_CONTAINER|MSGPACK_FLAG_ASSOC,\n449\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_map\n450\t\t},\n451\t\t{\n452\t\t\t\t0x90,\n453\t\t\t\t4,\n454\t\t\t\tmsgpack_fixarray,\n455\t\t\t\t0,\n456\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_FIXED|MSGPACK_FLAG_CONTAINER,\n457\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_array\n458\t\t},\n459\t\t{\n460\t\t\t\t0xd9,\n461\t\t\t\t8,\n462\t\t\t\tmsgpack_str8,\n463\t\t\t\t1,\n464\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_KEY,\n465\t\t\t\tucl_msgpack_parse_string\n466\t\t},\n467\t\t{\n468\t\t\t\t0xc4,\n469\t\t\t\t8,\n470\t\t\t\tmsgpack_bin8,\n471\t\t\t\t1,\n472\t\t\t\tMSGPACK_FLAG_KEY,\n473\t\t\t\tucl_m